## Repository

**GitHub**: <https://github.com/ronsway/MakeMyDay.git>

## Project Information

**ParentFlow** is a Hebrew-language parent communication system that automatically parses WhatsApp/email messages from schools and converts them into structured tasks and events, saving Israeli parents valuable time.

## Contributing

We welcome contributions from the community! Please see [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md) for guidelines on how to contribute to ParentFlow.

## Recognition

Special thanks to:

- The Israeli parent community for feedback and real-world testing
- Hebrew NLP research community for language processing insights
- Open source contributors whose libraries make this project possible

